claim.claim-text:
1. A battery structure comprising:
(a) a lithium anode for extracting lithium ions;
(b) a sulfur cathode for inserting said lithium ions;
(c) an electrolyte for transporting said lithium ions between said anode and said cathode; and
(d) a separator comprising a non-porous vanadium oxide layer that is electronically conductive and permeable to said lithium ions.
